    • Constructor Detail

      • Product

        public Product​(int id,
               String name,
               double price,
               int stock,
               int min,
               int max)
        Class constructor. Invoking will increment nextId.
        Parameters:
        id - The id of the new product as int. Usually set with getNextId().
        name - The name of the new product as String.
        price - The price of the new product as double.
        stock - The stock or inventory level of the product as int.
        min - The minimum inventory level as int.
        max - The maximum inventory level as int.
